<br>
I would love to be able to quickly memorize a set of spells for different situations or after being killed.  I could have a raid hotkey that will wipe my current spells memorized and then load up my favorite raid spells, then if I die during the raid, instead of finding the spells I want in my book, i could just press my hotkey.  Later when I'm ready to just get a xp group, i can press my xp group spell hotkey and be instantly ready.<br>
